<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-01-0287 </DOCNO><TEXT>The paper describes the development and sample use of a computer codewhich automates both the Monte Carlo and response surface approachesto probabilistic fuel performance modelling utilising the SLEUTH-82 deterministicprogram. A number of the statistical procedures employed, which havebeen prepared as independent computer codes, are also described. Theseare of general applicability in many areas of probabilistic assessment.</TEXT></DOC>